Package com.siperian.sif.message.metadata Description

Provides data objects for Siperian Hub meta-data - data describing objects defined in the Siperian Hub. These objects are returned by the listSiperianObjects and describeSiperianObject APIs.
See Also:
ListSiperianObjectsRequest, ListSiperianObjectsResponse, DescribeSiperianObjectRequest, DescribeSiperianObjectResponse
